General.Name: JonDeTech Sensors
General.Description: JonDeTech Sensors AB (publ) engages in the development of IR sensor detectors. It offers thermopiles for use in consumer electronics and IoT solutions, as well as in energy efficiency and safety applications, such as green technology, medtech, smart homes, and connected cities. The company has an agreement with OFILM Group Co., Ltd. for the development of presence detection module in laptops and digital door locks. JonDeTech Sensors AB (publ) was founded in 2008 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden.
